{"tid":207925,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"艾未未成功在北京開銀行戶口但被香港匯豐拒開戶   指「應實行一國一制」","createTime":"2017-04-19T07:59:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T17:02:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15090f8bea3b98127d68888a3b860f83bae0150c","tid":207925,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170419/19994340\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170419%2F19994340&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SjANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=fd03e872\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170419%2F19994340&h=91093719\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170419/19994340</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中國異見藝術家艾未未昨日在Instagram貼出一張匯豐銀行香港總行的黑白照，指自己身處香港，向匯豐申請開戶但被拒。他譏諷香港奉行「一國一制」可能更佳。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>指在京未被拒絕</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n艾未未在帖中寫道：「我身處香港，嘗試向匯豐銀行申請開戶，但被銀行總部以「商業決定」為由拒絕了。我在北京時從未遇到這種事情，或許實行「一國一制」更好。」（I'm in Hong Kong, trying to open an account at HSBC. My request was refused due to a&quot;commercial decision&quot; from the headquarter. This has not happened to me in Beijing. Maybe&quot;one country, one system&quot; is better.）<br />\n<br />\n事件曝光後，一眾網民在Twitter向艾未未了解情況，有人問及他是想開設個人戶口或是公司戶口，艾未未透露自己申請開設的是個人戶口。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者嘗試聯絡艾未未，惟其手機關機。匯豐銀行昨日回覆《蘋果》查詢時表示，基於私隱理由，不會針對個別客人或賬戶作出評論，但強調該行不會因為個人的政治立場，而拒絕開戶。<br />\n現年59歲的艾未未，多次參與公民運動，引起北京當局關注。2011年，艾在北京首都機場準備前往香港時被帶走，當局其後指其嫌「經濟犯罪」而在接受調查，事件引起國際關注而「獲釋」，其間艾被非法關押81天。<br />\n<br />\n■記者吳秀麗"},{"pid":"b4135fb990d9efe555bad869460f06ec9247dd09","tid":207925,"uid":470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:01:51.000Z","msg":"你又唔係帶一千幾百個嚟，做乜要拿屎上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺北京無問題係因為支那嘅銀行已經直接connect黨嘅系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b7a067ab1d9c223ecfd184420d2dca1d87b021","tid":207925,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:05:42.000Z","msg":"就係因為香港係「一國兩制」, 先有唔同開戶準則囉<br />\n<br />\n唔開戶比佢, 佢就話要「一國一制」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4caf00c547a8899b6fd1365fa4283ad1bad5dc40","tid":207925,"uid":34838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:08:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就係因為香港係「一國兩制」, 先有唔同開戶準則囉<br />\n<br />\n唔開戶比佢, 佢就話要「一國一制」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁實行「一國一制」佢咪喺香港開到戶囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6986c9b603956a8a45f9f12e26f0355603a3a895","tid":207925,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就係因為香港係「一國兩制」, 先有唔同開戶準則囉<br />\n<br />\n唔開戶比佢, 佢就話要「一國一制」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁實行「一國一制」佢咪喺香港開到戶囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以呢D所謂「支那維權人士」, 根本都係侵略香港既殖民者黎<br />\n<br />\n同溫雲超一鳩樣"},{"pid":"bb9adda3b242a15ccf29a07317f31e990e307844","tid":207925,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:11:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"242608f3702b5ed4c1c27ff02b6cc3a5e6b51366","tid":207925,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就係因為香港係「一國兩制」, 先有唔同開戶準則囉<br />\n<br />\n唔開戶比佢, 佢就話要「一國一制」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家好多國家既人係香港，個人戶口又好公司又好都好難開戶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學術討論：如果我個人幫大陸朋友開個戶口畀佢用有冇問題？"},{"pid":"d0472d24c2db57c71a8867659cbbdb71062685ff","tid":207925,"uid":22559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T08:12:55.000Z","msg":"以為轉用外資銀行就無限制<br />\n點知連大貓都唔比開"},{"